casebody.data:
First Department,

November, 1969

(November 6, 1969) Arnold D. Roseman, Respondent, v. Morton Rosenberg et al., Appellants.

Order entered March 17, 1969, unanimously affirmed, without costs and without disbursements. This determination is without prejudice to an application, to be made following completion of examinations of parties, for an examination before trial of the nonparty witnesses. Concur- — -Eager, J. P., Tilzer, McGivern, Markewich and Steuer, JJ.
